    tc.sample_identifier as sample_id,
    fd.customer_id,
    fd.current_credit_limit,
    fd.credit_card_type,
    fd.state
FROM (SELECT 'E4LZGN2AUHCTISS7O9' as sample_identifier) tc
LEFT JOIN public.fry14m_scheduled1_data fd 
    ON tc.sample_identifier = fd.customer_id
